Wok Stars - Season 1, Episode 10




Final Cook-Off: Part 2

The final 2 cooks are given a one-on-one mentoring session with Chef Alvin and Chef Willin to improve and enhance their signature dishes. Both cooks then met with Koufu and Q'SON to design their stalls and new signage, and compete to become the ultimate Wok Star.




Original Air Date: 26-Mar-2014
